      ],
      "updated": 1772103325173,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "If something goes wrong \n    -> dispatch alert through write() \n    -> SSL_accept returns -1\n    -> shutdown(socket_fd, SHUT_WR)\n    -> exhaust buffer by calling several read() until\nreceive EOF\nIf everything is Okay -> SSL_accept return 1",
      "fontSize": 28.54584966146722,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If something goes wrong \n    -> dispatch alert through write() \n    -> SSL_accept returns -1\n    -> shutdown(socket_fd, SHUT_WR)\n    -> exhaust buffer by calling several read() until receive EOF\nIf everything is Okay -> SSL_accept return 1",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1cYJmga29ByF3Kl_LTufF",
